Version 1.0.0 Alpha
* Improve speed of data/config collection.
* Fix the add storage drive dialog in the active MD device view.
* Dynamic add storage drive to grow the MD array, when storage devices are removed thay do not appear in the available devices.
* Show used/free space of MD device
* Re-format for coding style PEP8
* Hide the default RAID (mdadm) plugin when this plugin becomes active.

